---
import Layout from '../layouts/layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Industries">

<main class="bg-gray-900 text-white min-h-screen">

<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-24 text-center">

<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-blue-400">
Industries We Secure
</h1>

<p class="mt-4 text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
Select your industry to discover cybersecurity solutions and OEM technologies tailored to your infrastructure and security needs.
</p>

</section>
<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 pb-24">

<div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">

<a href="/industries/manufacturing">

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-blue-400 hover:scale-105 transition">

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">
Manufacturing
</h2>

<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-300">
Protect OT systems, endpoints, and sensitive industrial data.
</p>

<div class="mt-4 text-xs text-gray-400">

<p>Security Domains:</p>

<ul class="mt-1 space-y-1">
<li>• Data Loss Prevention</li>
<li>• Endpoint Detection</li>
<li>• Vulnerability Management</li>
</ul>

<p class="mt-3">Recommended Vendors:</p>

<p class="text-blue-400">
Forcepoint · Trellix · SentinelOne
</p>

</div>

</div>

</a>

<a href="/industries/healthcare">

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-blue-400 hover:scale-105 transition">

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">
Healthcare
</h2>

<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-300">
Secure patient records, medical devices, and hospital infrastructure.
</p>

<div class="mt-4 text-xs text-gray-400">

<p>Security Domains:</p>

<ul class="mt-1 space-y-1">
<li>• Data Loss Prevention</li>
<li>• Endpoint Detection & Response</li>
<li>• Vulnerability Management</li>
<li>• Identity & Access Management (PAM)</li>
</ul>

<p class="mt-3">Recommended Vendors:</p>

<p class="text-blue-400">Forcepoint · SentinelOne · ARCON · Trellix</p>

</div>

</div>

</a>

<a href="/industries/banking">
<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-blue-400 hover:scale-105 transition">
<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">Banking & Finance</h2>
<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-300">
Protect financial transactions and prevent fraud and breaches.
</p>

<div class="mt-4 text-xs text-gray-400">
<p>Security Domains:</p>
<ul class="mt-1 space-y-1">
<li>• Fraud Detection & Transaction Monitoring</li>
<li>• Data Loss Prevention</li>
<li>• Endpoint Detection</li>
<li>• Privileged Access Management</li>
</ul>
<p class="mt-3">Recommended Vendors:</p>
<p class="text-blue-400">Trellix · Forcepoint · ARCON · Tenable</p>
</div>

</div>
</a>

<a href="/industries/education">
<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-blue-400 hover:scale-105 transition">
<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">Education</h2>
<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-300">
Secure research data, student records, and campus networks.
</p>

<div class="mt-4 text-xs text-gray-400">
<p>Security Domains:</p>
<ul class="mt-1 space-y-1">
<li>• Network Segmentation & Access Control</li>
<li>• Endpoint Security</li>
<li>• Identity Management</li>
<li>• Data Protection</li>
</ul>
<p class="mt-3">Recommended Vendors:</p>
<p class="text-blue-400">Forcepoint · SentinelOne · ARCON · Tenable</p>
</div>

</div>
</a>

<a href="/industries/it-saas">
<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-blue-400 hover:scale-105 transition">
<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">IT & SaaS</h2>
<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-300">
Protect cloud infrastructure, APIs, and digital platforms.
</p>

<div class="mt-4 text-xs text-gray-400">
<p>Security Domains:</p>
<ul class="mt-1 space-y-1">
<li>• Cloud Security & CSPM</li>
<li>• API Protection</li>
<li>• Identity & Access Management</li>
<li>• Vulnerability Management</li>
</ul>
<p class="mt-3">Recommended Vendors:</p>
<p class="text-blue-400">Tenable · ARCON · Trellix · SentinelOne</p>
</div>

</div>
</a>

<a href="/industries/government">
<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-blue-400 hover:scale-105 transition">
<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">Government</h2>
<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-300">
Secure critical infrastructure and public sector data systems.
</p>

<div class="mt-4 text-xs text-gray-400">
<p>Security Domains:</p>
<ul class="mt-1 space-y-1">
<li>• Critical Infrastructure Protection</li>
<li>• Incident Response & Forensics</li>
<li>• Endpoint Detection</li>
<li>• Data Sovereignty & DLP</li>
</ul>
<p class="mt-3">Recommended Vendors:</p>
<p class="text-blue-400">Trellix · Forcepoint · ARCON · Tenable</p>
</div>

</div>
</a>

</div>

</section>

</main>

</Layout>